00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:59,000
We decide instead that
we would like to be able

229
00:18:59,149 --> 00:19:06,200
to filter this visualization by
chain as well as the visualization

230
00:19:06,201 --> 00:19:12,920
on the reg versus markdown
report page and the KPI report page.

231
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:17,920
We'd like to use a visual
filter known as a slicer.

232
00:19:18,219 --> 00:19:21,800
So what I'm gonna do is I'm
gonna make room for the slicer.

233
00:19:22,720 --> 00:19:25,884
On this page, I'm gonna just
leave more space on the right

234
00:19:25,885 --> 00:19:31,280
side where I'll be able to
pop the slicer visualization in.

235
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:33,920
And since we're gonna
wanna use the same slicer

236
00:19:33,921 --> 00:19:38,920
on two other report pages,
KPI and reg versus markdown,

237
00:19:39,019 --> 00:19:42,600
go to each of those pages and
leave about the same amount

238
00:19:42,749 --> 00:19:45,980
of space on the right
side of those visualizations.

239
00:19:47,629 --> 00:19:53,800
When you're done making those adjustments,
come back to your TYLY and variants page.

240
00:19:54,624 --> 00:19:57,780
Make sure your
visualization is not selected.

