00:27:44,755 --> 00:27:49,520
drill-through field, so I'm
gonna locate it in the fields pane.

338
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:52,840
I'm gonna click and
hold and drag it to the box

339
00:27:52,841 --> 00:27:59,180
that says add drill-through fields here
