341
00:28:08,769 --> 00:28:13,540
Also, on your multi-row
card, you have a back button.

342
00:28:13,541 --> 00:28:18,573
That's a navigation button
that you can use to go back to

343
00:28:18,574 --> 00:28:22,080
whatever report page you
performed the drill-through on.

344
00:28:23,679 --> 00:28:26,740
Let's go ahead and save our file.

345
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:34,920
We'll circle back to formatting the multi-row
card, but right now, we wanna proceed

346
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:39,200
so you can see the
functionality of using drill-through.

347
00:28:39,201 --> 00:28:44,060
We're gonna create a stacked
bar chart on a new page.

348
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:51,000
Go ahead and create a new page,
and name that page Sales by Category.

349
00:28:55,399 --> 00:28:59,480
In your visualizations
pane, the stacked bar chart

