351
00:29:01,841 --> 00:29:07,220
Go ahead and locate it and click on
it to put the framework on the canvas.

352
00:29:09,069 --> 00:29:14,020
From the item table,
we're gonna drag Category

353
00:29:14,269 --> 00:29:18,080
to the access box in
the visualizations pane,

354
00:29:20,104 --> 00:29:25,328
and we're gonna drag from
the sales table this year's

