00:29:25,329 --> 00:29:32,540
sales value to the values
box in the visualizations pane,

356
00:29:33,639 --> 00:29:36,680
and we have our stacked bar chart.

357
00:29:38,079 --> 00:29:41,520
Now, I'm gonna make the
bar chart just a little bit wider,

358
00:29:41,521 --> 00:29:46,760
and we'll come back and format it
later, and I'm gonna click away from it

359
00:29:46,761 --> 00:29:50,520
because we wanna add
two slicers to this page,

