00:29:51,960 --> 00:29:55,280
one for chain and one for buyer.

361
00:29:55,329 --> 00:30:01,720
So in your visualizations pane,
locate your slicer icon and click on it,

362
00:30:03,219 --> 00:30:08,120
and I'm gonna just move the slicer
over to the right side of the canvas.

363
00:30:08,121 --> 00:30:11,400
It doesn't need to be as wide as it is,

364
00:30:12,549 --> 00:30:15,120
and you can size yours accordingly.

365
00:30:20,659 --> 00:30:23,748
So I'm gonna just pop
it over here on the right

366
00:30:23,749 --> 00:30:27,580
side, and you'll notice
the red dashed lines.

