368
00:30:30,705 --> 00:30:32,840
So when the line is on the bottom,

369
00:30:32,841 --> 00:30:36,980
it means it's aligned with
the bottom of the visualization,

370
00:30:41,104 --> 00:30:44,080
and I'm gonna go to the store table

371
00:30:44,879 --> 00:30:49,440
and drag chain into the slicer,

372
00:30:52,309 --> 00:30:56,780
and we decide that we want the slicer,
instead of having everything displayed

