Make that one a drop-down as well.

386
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:21,760
(mouse clicking)

387
00:32:21,761 --> 00:32:25,960
And for right now, I'm gonna just
move the buyer one down a little bit.

388
00:32:29,009 --> 00:32:31,860
We're gonna go ahead and save our file,

389
00:32:35,309 --> 00:32:37,960
and then we'll explore
