00:33:00,514 --> 00:33:03,640
have men's, shoes, these
are the different categories,

395
00:33:04,989 --> 00:33:08,040
now that we have a drill-through page,

396
00:33:08,041 --> 00:33:11,360
we'll see drill-through
on the right-click menu.

397
00:33:11,409 --> 00:33:15,173
So what I'm gonna do, and it
even tells you that when you

