01:25:39,270 --> 01:25:45,460
So the push data set, all of them update
in real time as the data is pushed in.

1049
01:25:46,660 --> 01:25:49,180
You'll notice that the push method

1050
01:25:50,030 --> 01:25:56,020
allows data to be stored permanently
in Power BI for historic analysis.

1051
01:25:56,021 --> 01:26:00,120
When it's streaming, the
data is only temporarily stored

1052
01:26:00,121 --> 01:26:06,100
for an hour to render visuals, and
pub nub doesn't store any data at all.

1053
01:26:07,125 --> 01:26:12,140
Because the data is stored
permanently for the push method,

1054
01:26:12,190 --> 01:26:16,760
you can use your Power
